{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "ops_and_training", "channel": "sop_updates", "user": "jane_smith", "message": "Just a reminder for everyone to review the updated customer service SOPs before our meeting tomorrow.", "created_at": 1620502400000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "knowledge_management", "channel": "system_upgrades", "user": "john_doe", "message": "The inventory system issue has been resolved. Everything's back to normal now.", "created_at": 1620503000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "knowledge_management", "channel": "system_upgrades", "user": "sophie_tran", "message": "Hello team, as part of our Knowledge Management System report for September 2025, I've noticed an interesting trend. We've been working closely with the IT department to streamline and improve our database. As of now, around 12% of the IT staff is directly involved in developing and upgrading the knowledge management database. This collaboration has been instrumental in ensuring the efficiency and relevancy of our system.", "create_at": 1620500000000}}
